# Patterns without ** only match at the context root, and the build context is
# the repo root — so the nested real secrets file needs naming explicitly, or it
# is baked into every image layer at /app/deploy/hetzner/svrz-api.env.
*.env
.env*
**/*.env
**/.env*
deploy/hetzner/pb_data
deploy/hetzner/.env
deploy/hetzner/svrz-api.env
deploy/hetzner/svrz-api.env.example
# Activity-log JSONL carries user identities and IP addresses.
**/logs
logs
# "actual secret values" by its own instructions.
infrastructure.private.md
